Node runs JavaScript outside the browser 
(A) Javascript can be used to build Real-time Networking Applications like Chats, Video streaming services, command line tools (B) It can be used to add interactive behaviour to web pages. (C) It can be used in game development (D) JavaScript can also be used for web development on the server. (E) JavaScript is also an excellent language for working with AI.
